## Reference
http://xmodulo.com/configure-rsyslog-client-centos.html
https://linux.cn/article-4835-1.html

1) check rsyslog
rpm -qa | grep rsyslog

rsyslogd -v

2) rsyslog install on centos
yum install rsyslog

3) rsyslog restart after configration changes
#centos7 systemctl restart rsyslog.service
#centos6 service rsyslog restart
